narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: DO IT. GRADUATE WITH A SKILL.

If you're interested in photography beyond an introductory class, definitely take it. It will be much smaller than an intro class, which allows for closer bonds between classmates and more time for the professor to focus on your work individually.

I would definitely recommend Art 237 but it requires the student to be willing to put a lot of time and effort into the subject. If you push yourself you will be able to profit fully from Professor Kereszi's lectures and encouragement.
